    "client_msg_id": "0c02855a-6e44-48eb-a5e5-1624ceb384f0",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "<@U5TCAFTD3> I second Flappy Bird. It forces consideration of how to make graphics (beyond traditional HTML pages) accessible. APIs are as important as a language itself (and the design of the language affects the design of the APIs).",
    "user": "UCGAK10LS",
    "ts": "1565823027.043300",
