  {
    "client_msg_id": "F6349D68-235A-42AD-A9B5-1FA423F45357",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "Good point. In fact, when I saw this new channel, my first reaction was “what the heck is an end-user?” There are so many different kinds of non-programmers using computers.",
    "user": "UJBAJNFLK",
    "ts": "1565844934.069000",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "source_team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "user_profile": {
      "avatar_hash": "e169f54bbaf8",
      "image_72": "https://avatars.slack-edge.com/2021-03-12/1859691333940_e169f54bbaf8b9b36b12_72.png",
      "first_name": "Konrad",
      "real_name": "Konrad Hinsen",
